FUCK!!!!! but anyway, i talked to jen today, apparently me and her are still doing the whoe freinds with benefits thing, and well, thats cool. i also talked to the other jenni, the one who lives in missouri, she was one of my best friends, and its so hard to get a hold of her, but i did, and i was catching up with her, im supposed to call her a lil bit later, i dont know if i will. but anyways, i gotta go, i will see you later.

hello everyone, how are u? im alright i guess, this weekend has been kind of bitter sweet. it started with me wasting all of friday night and saturday morning trying to hurry to finish some last minute government work, but i finally finished it. then i was supposed to go to a party on saturday night at around midnight, but when i called to see if it was still going on, no one answered there phone. o well, so i didnt sleep at all that night, i stayed up all night and watched movies. so on sunday i hung out with kenny and danielle kennys birthday, he ended up going out to dinner with his mom, so i took danielle out for dinner at little daddys, i think she liked it, and it was nice cause we actually had a chance to talk for awhile. but other then that, i went and searched for a job, ith no success again. o well, i gotta go, ill see ya later.

so, ive finally been caught, this entire school year, or well for most of it anyway, ive been driving to and fro from school, well i dont wanna pay to park at the school, so ive been coming up with things to throw off the security guards u know. and until today, ive been getting away with it. first i parked in different parking lots to throw them off, one day i would park in the student lot, another day i would park in the staff lot, and so on and so on, well after awhile the security became aware of this little trick, so before they could write me a ticket for it, i found a kid and took one of his parking passes, and that worked for a little over a month or so u know, well the problem with that is that all the passes are number-coded, so i knew it wasnt a permanent fixture, i just thought i had more time, well they found me out somehow, and they told me today that i had to get a real one or i wouldnt be allowed to park there. so i guess i must concede, they did tell me that i was one of the longest times anyone had ever went without being caught, so that makes me kinda proud, but o well, ill talk to u all later

so, today was just another run of the mill boring school day, but other then that my life has been pretty much all shit. do u ever have one of those times in ur life where everything doesnt seem so bad and ur almost oblivious to all thats around u, well i think ive been having one of those periods for the last six or seven months and now i beleive its drawing to an end. i dont want it to, but i dont think i really have a choice. im starting to feel my old ways creeping up on me. i dont want them, i was fine without them, but with each passing day i find it harder and harder to keep my old depressing feelings at bay. i dont know what im gonna do, ive tried talking about it, ive tried ignoring it, but nothing seems to work. i think the reason is that i truly dont know the reason why i feel this way, and everything just seems so hopeless, i dont know what im gonna do, ive got to many things i have to do, to many people are relying on me, i just wish i could rely on someone like they rely on me, i cant talk about whats bothering me cause i dont know what it is. it seems hopeless.

so, i cant sleep again, i dont know why i am unable to sleep for more then 5 hours. it sure would be nice to not fall asleep in school everyonce in a while. i hate it. today has been full of odd circumstances. but u know what, for the first time, i dont care. im gonna see jen tomorrow, and really thats all i can think about. not because of anything sexual we might do, but because im genuinely excited to dee her, i miss her a whole lot. i'd give anything just to be able to hold her in my arms forever. i love her more then anything. she fills my life with joy, and every time i talk to her, i feel the warmest feeling, i feel secure. does that make me sound a little gay? o well, i have to fucking find out when homecoming is, no one can tell me for sure, im freaking out. and will someone please tell me whats up with this bullshit, the quiz, its stupid. poeple keep asking me to take there quizes. i refuse to take another quiz, unless u make one with truly worthy, thought provoking questions.
